fortext,predinzip(cleaned,preds.tolist()):
ifnotisinstance(text,str)ornottext.strip():

max_vals=df_songs[numeric_cols].max()

thresholds={
col:[
min_vals[col]+span[col]*0.2,
min_vals[col]+span[col]*0.4,
min_vals[col]+span[col]*0.6,
min_vals[col]+span[col]*0.8,
]
forcolinnumeric_cols
}
bucket_labels=["verylow","low","medium","high","veryhigh"]
#Bucketlabeling
defbucket_label(col,val):
th=thresholds[col]
ifval<=th[0]:
returnbucket_labels[0]
elifval<=th[1]:
returnbucket_labels[1]
elifval<=th[2]:
returnbucket_labels[2]
elifval<=th[3]:
returnbucket_labels[3]
else:
returnbucket_labels[4]

parts.append(f"{desc}{col.replace('_','')}")
forcolintext_cols:
parts.append(f"{col.replace('_','')}is{row[col]}")
return";".join(parts)+"."

#PlaylistGeneratorv3
defgenerate_playlist_v3(
prompt:str,
df_songs:pd.DataFrame,
all_tags:set,
popularity_pref:str='all',
artist_pop_pref:str='all',
year_min:int=None,
year_max:int=None,
alpha:float=0.6,
beta:float=0.2,
gamma:float=0.2,
top_k:int=20
)->pd.DataFrame:
filtered=filter_songs(
df_songs,
popularity_pref,
artist_pop_pref,
year_min,
year_max
).reset_index(drop=True)
user_emb=embed_prompt(prompt)
song_matrix=np.vstack(filtered['ft_embedding'])
sims=util.cos_sim(user_emb,song_matrix)[0].cpu().numpy()
sim_scores=(sims+1.0)/2.0
raw_tags=match_tags_from_prompt(prompt,all_tags)
matched_tags=prune_matched_tags(raw_tags)
genre_flags=filtered['genres'].apply(
lambdags:1.0ifany(tingsfortinmatched_tags)else0.0
).values
matched_langs=guess_languages_from_prompt(prompt)
lang_flags=filtered['language'].apply(
lambdaL:1.0ifLinmatched_langselse0.0
).values
final_scores=(
alpha*sim_scores+
beta*genre_flags+
gamma*lang_flags
)
idxs=np.argsort(final_scores)[::-1][:top_k]
out=filtered.iloc[idxs].copy()
out['language']=filtered['language'].iloc[idxs]
out['score']=final_scores[idxs]
returnout[['song_name','name_artist','language','score']]

defretrieve_with_numeric_boost(prompt:str,top_k:int=20,alpha:float=0.8):
